QuestData.Title: Orako's Report
QuestData.Description: <You remind Orako that he was supposed to send a report back to Captain Verne.>$b$bRight, a report. All that I've seen here is fish. Lots and lots of fish.$b$b<Orako looks over at the sack of fish that you brought for him.>$b$bBring this back to the captain. This is my report.
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver Orako's Report to Captain "Jewels" Verne in Tenebrous Cavern.
QuestData.RewardText: This is his report?! That idiot...$b$bI suppose we can use the food. Thanks, $n. You've done as well as can be expected.
